name: Discovery: Monolith II
description: Guilty and gratitude are always be a part of me, and a lot of people too. For me it's just...sometimes I feel like so thankful for what people gift to me and at the same time I feel bad because I can't give them in return, or the other time I just make mistake and disappoint them. This is not a poetry, just a bunch of words trying to explain that I'm not good at saying thank you and sorry. I'm sorry.
